summary: This is the start of my mod. I put it up right now so the other people in my mod team can see what I\'m working with so far
descriptionHtml:
So For my mod team this is what you do to get inside this mod in it\'s current state.

1.) Add file to your Skyrim Data file.
2.) Open Skyrim and type coc LZLCavesofZesima.
3.) Tell me how long it takes you to get through the first maze. The end of the first maze is a huge room with nothing in it. Thanks for your help thus far

4.)If you want to be part of the team PM me. Thanks for your time.
author: Faria400
